'''Nahra''' was a [[Kaminoan/Legends|Kaminoan]] form of ballet in which the species used their bodies to show emotions typically withheld. Using Nahra, Kaminoans mimed their analog of the emotion; outside viewers considered the dance to be somewhat disturbing, due to the Kaminoans' almost total lack of emotion understanding.

